  <data key="d0">Kai Ji Ren Shu</data>
  <data key="d1">organization</data>
  <data key="d2">Kai Ji Ren Shu is an organization that has been the subject of various maintenance activities and records. The company, which has a branch in Taichung, requires regular maintenance to ensure its operations run smoothly. This maintenance involves version upgrades and configuration checks. Kai Ji Ren Shu's maintenance needs are well-documented, with multiple records indicating the organization's commitment to upkeep and operational efficiency.&lt;SEP&gt;Kai Ji Ren Shu is an organization that underwent maintenance as recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;Kai Ji Ren Shu is a company that has undergone maintenance as documented in the record.&lt;SEP&gt;Kai Ji Ren Shu is a company that requires maintenance, as documented in the record.&lt;SEP&gt;Kai Ji Ren Shu is an organization that requires maintenance, as documented in the record.&lt;SEP&gt;Kai Ji Ren Shu is the subject of a maintenance record.&lt;SEP&gt;Kai Ji Ren Shu is the subject of a maintenance record.</data>
