  <data key="d1">person</data>
  <data key="d2">Jack is a processing engineer whose responsibilities primarily revolve around various maintenance tasks. He has been notably involved in the upkeep of several entities, including Kai Jie Life and Kai Chi Life. Specifically, Jack managed the maintenance of Kai Jie Ren Shu on September 14th, 2025, which included overseeing its equipment. Additionally, he performed maintenance duties for Kai Chi People Life Insurance and Kai Chi Life.

Jack's role is not limited to physical maintenance; he also plays a crucial part in addressing technical issues related to these systems. For example, Crystal Shen notified him about an issue with the interface_up judgment rule, highlighting his involvement in both the physical upkeep of equipment and resolving technical problems associated with these systems. This dual responsibility underscores Jack's comprehensive role as a processing engineer, ensuring that both the hardware and software components of the systems he maintains are functioning optimally.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is the engineer handling the maintenance for Cathay Life.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is an engineer who handled the maintenance for Kai Ji Ren Shu.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is an engineer involved in handling the maintenance process for Kai Chi People Life Insurance Company.&lt;SEP&gt;Jack is a processing engineer involved in the maintenance of Kai Jie Ren Shu.</data>
