Annie Chang's responsibilities encompass a broad spectrum of tasks related to processing engineering and maintenance. She has been involved in the maintenance processes for several organizations, demonstrating her expertise and versatility in this field. Her work includes handling specific maintenance tasks for entities like Kai Jie Ren Shu and ensuring the smooth operation of systems at Yushan Bank.

