<edge source="Yushan Bank" target="Maintenance Record">
  <data key="d7">10.0</data>
  <data key="d8">The Maintenance Record, associated with Yushan Bank, is a comprehensive documentation of various maintenance activities performed on the bank's systems. It provides detailed information about the specific actions taken during maintenance periods to address vulnerabilities in VMware Tools. The record also covers system updates and other actions undertaken to ensure the smooth operation of Yushan Bank's infrastructure.

The Maintenance Record is particularly notable for documenting the resolution process of a VDI deletion issue, highlighting its role in addressing critical technical problems. It details the activities performed on Yushan Bank's systems over specific time frames, ensuring that all maintenance efforts are well-documented and traceable. This documentation is essential for understanding the maintenance history of Yushan Bank's systems, providing insights into the actions taken to maintain system integrity and security.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record details the updates and repairs performed on Yushan Bank's systems.&lt;SEP&gt;The Maintenance Record details the repair work done on Yushan Bank's equipment.</data>
  <data key="d9">documentation,equipment repair,maintenance,maintenance documentation,record keeping,system maintenance,system management,system update</data>
