<edge source="World Athletics Federation" target="Noah Carter">
  <data key="d7">172.0</data>
  <data key="d8">Noah Carter, in relation to the World Athletics Federation, has achieved significant recognition for his exceptional athletic abilities. The World Athletics Federation officially validated Noah Carter's new 100-meter (100m) sprint record during a championship event. This validation process by the federation ensures that Carter's achievement is officially recognized, highlighting his remarkable speed and athleticism in the 100m sprint.

The validation of Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record underscores the importance of this milestone in his athletic career. Multiple sources confirm the validation of Carter's record-breaking performance at the championship, emphasizing the significance of this achievement. The World Athletics Federation has consistently validated Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set during the championship, reinforcing the legitimacy and importance of his accomplishment.

The repeated validation from the federation solidifies Carter's reputation as a leading athlete in the sport. The World Athletics Federation oversees the validation process, ensuring that Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record is officially acknowledged and validated. This official recognition by the World Athletics Federation underscores Noah Carter's status as a top athlete in the field of athletics.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.&lt;SEP&gt;The World Athletics Federation validates Noah Carter's new 100m sprint record set at the championship.</data>
